WHEREAS, Section 2 of Article XXIV of the Oklahoma Constitution
20
21
requires that a proposal to hold a Constitutional Convention shall
21
22
be submitted to a vote of the people at least once every twenty (20)
22
23
years; and
23
24
24
Req. No. 2834 Page 1

1
